{"tid":2202989,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"侍應涉藏雷射筆 辯方斥警員說謊","createTime":"2020-09-15T04:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T04:45:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f444bd713039009040a60ca5a2f797109c1a6ce3","tid":2202989,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:39:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/MTL2QH35LNCW5NR42LPCQCFN5M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FMTL2QH35LNCW5NR42LPCQCFN5M%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacUV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=7c843e3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FMTL2QH35LNCW5NR42LPCQCFN5M%2F&h=7e617f72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/MTL2QH35LNCW5NR42LPCQCFN5M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n侍應涉藏雷射筆 辯方斥警員說謊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5xvEseiOgAAe8FBqbfW-IzxNLyY=/1775x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BESUXG7CFFE4ZGT7K3XZGBOZ5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5xvEseiOgAAe8FBqbfW-IzxNLyY%3D%2F1775x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBESUXG7CFFE4ZGT7K3XZGBOZ5Y.jpg&h=eefb4ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員陳樂謙指去年10月30日在屯門衝突中追截被告。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方屯門大興行動基地去年10月30日疑有不明氣體洩漏，大批市民上街抗議。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片段證沒掙扎逃跑<br />\n<br />\n被告陳戩曄否認參與非法集結及在公眾地⽅管有攻擊性武器兩罪，但承認沒在規定下出示身份證明文件罪。<br />\n<br />\n警員陳樂謙（譯音）供稱，當時示威者在良德街堵路，未有應警方警告離開。他從防線追向身處人群的被告，從後捉住被告的手並扯其衣服。被告起初掙扎及逃跑，及後在其他警員出手下終遭制服。<br />\n<br />\n然而，辯方播出現場影片，顯示警員並非從後截停被告，而是面對面接觸；而被告亦沒掙扎，更向警員謂：「喂，街坊喎！乜事𠵱家？」<br />\n<br />\n警員否認截停被告時是面對面，僅同意是「側面」，又改口稱「被告個身左右搖擺」，但他同意影片拍不到被告身體左右擺動。辯方直指警員說謊。案件表證成立，今日結案陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC613/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u2mt4KKnfjSxnBVvqa2DQNHhPrw=/1319x1319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PWNQTEGICJFRHDAGMQY6FCJKKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu2mt4KKnfjSxnBVvqa2DQNHhPrw%3D%2F1319x1319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPWNQTEGICJFRHDAGMQY6FCJKKY.jpg&h=471bf88c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員陳樂謙"},{"pid":"fdc37559641589fd321b41a1378352160963c524","tid":2202989,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"軍火"},{"pid":"336db4af168ed2ab4339fc5344afd15980c04240","tid":2202989,"uid":189650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:42:02.000Z","msg":"警謊冇後果，有片仲死撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f8d62ed2c822fb7d54e9bc5f089bdd26054309","tid":2202989,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:45:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/79217/org/df9030d1d8e0b99f0ecfcce185ae82b8.jpg/LCz7HkgdmP5ucBKu4DsQ6rh3IqaAWgFdAEMGSgBDBko?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F79217%2Forg%2Fdf9030d1d8e0b99f0ecfcce185ae82b8.jpg%2FLCz7HkgdmP5ucBKu4DsQ6rh3IqaAWgFdAEMGSgBDBko%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e9792681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳樂謙陳詠謙係咪兩兄弟???"}]}